snippet.title: Taiko No Tatsujin 3 PS2 Opening Intro Movie
snippet.description:
More Taiko Openings on my Channel!

This is the opening movie to the third Taiko no Tatsujin PS2 game: Taiko no Tatsujin: Appare Sandaime

Directly converted from the original disc for your pleasure.

Enjoy.

太鼓の達人 あっぱれ三代目のOP
